Specifically wrt the compression layer, there's a small table here:
https://github.com/mlin/sqlite_zstd_vfs#performance
(The Genomics Extension sets up good defaults for the many obscure tuning
settings discussed there.)
I'd welcome suggestions for other benchmarking aspects of interest. It's
usually going to be a bit nuanced of course, to compare a super flexible
tool like SQLite to code dedicated to specific problems & formats!
